'''Bucloc''' is a 6th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Abra province|Abra]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 2,109 people in 357 households.

==Deng Barangay==

Bucloc is politically subdivided into 4 [[barangay]]s.

* Ducligan
* Labaan
* Lingay
* Lamao (Pob.)

